{"tid":41982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[矮撚入] 有咩慘得過向南韓/歐美生得矮既人????","createTime":"2016-12-16T09:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T04:55:44.000Z","uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf498f7f39f8039e6e6e767f71917f5e4b71d36","tid":41982,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"我得178 著埋鞋181左右<br />\n<br />\n前排去首爾,.屌你老母成條街有一半多D仔高過我...屌撚死佢地咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時香港起碼我高過6成仔..<br />\n<br />\n咁都未算最仆街<br />\n1年前, 住LA個姑媽個女結婚, 我地成家飛左一轉美國去參加婚禮...<br />\n班死鬼佬個個185以上...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我向佢地身邊影相, 同一個小朋友冇咩分別, 好撚自卑。向唐人街以外既地方, 個個高我半個頭...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係後悔春青期果陣 冇打藍球搞到宜家咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d51aeb390ce379287f75f81b92c7b4d9b6c4116","tid":41982,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:50:37.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國短人來到香港<br />\n突變中等身材"},{"pid":"cb34b80c78248dbd1aeb2c9a2f68f52908637b60","tid":41982,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"仲有, 去支那北方(東北三省)D人又係好高好屈機, 不過佢地唔係鬼佬樣/韓仔打扮, 通常都係肥壯TYPE, 變相冇咁自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e090d79e218768f02146893e454f998bff71f0","tid":41982,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國短人來到香港<br />\n突變中等身材</blockquote><br />\n加埋鬼佬樣, 溝死晒D港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b2c62b5bceaea3f240e084e3e9a3c20865d04c","tid":41982,"uid":43358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"連登冇晒矮撚喇, 入黎圍爐傾計啦<im